Organization

An organization admin can open organization **Settings** , go to the **Privacy** section, and activate **Enforce default code saving restrictions** so code saving stays off by default for every team. While this enforcement is active, team admins canŌĆÖt turn on **Enable code saving by default** for a team. For the full list of organization controls, see [Enforce privacy settings for all teams](/platform/hosting/privacy-settings#enforce-privacy-settings-for-all-teams).

## 

